[Cite as 09/05/2003 Case Announcements #2, 2003-0hio-4691.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

September 5, 2003

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2003-1576. State v. Gann.

Butler App. No. CA2002-05-110, 2003-0hio-4000. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of court of appeals’ judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents.
